---
title: Speedy Spag Bol with Parsley Crumb and Cheese
description: This Speedy Spag Bol is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/speedy-spag-bol-bf32a03d-1df20e52.jpg
